import React from "react";
import {
  AddressCheckout,
  AddressDiv,
  BagCheckout,
  CartItems,
  CartLeft,
  CartRight,
  ChangeButton,
  Container,
  DeliverTo,
  DotsCheckout,
  Logo,
  NavCheckOutSteps,
  NavContainer,
  NavLogo,
  NavSecure,
  PaymentCheckout,
  SecureLogo,
  SecureN,
} from "./Cart.element";

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <NavContainer>
        <NavLogo>
          <Logo src="https://images.indianexpress.com/2021/01/myntra.png" />
        </NavLogo>
        <NavCheckOutSteps>
          <BagCheckout>BAG</BagCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <AddressCheckout>ADDRESS</AddressCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <PaymentCheckout>PAYMENT</PaymentCheckout>
        </NavCheckOutSteps>
        <NavSecure>
          <SecureLogo src="https://constant.myntassets.com/checkout/assets/img/sprite-secure.png" />
          <SecureN>100% SECURE</SecureN>
        </NavSecure>
      </NavContainer>
      <CartItems>
        <CartLeft>

            <AddressDiv>
                <DeliverTo>Deliver To:</DeliverTo>
                <ChangeButton>CHANGE ADDRESS</ChangeButton>
            </AddressDiv>

            
        </CartLeft>
        <CartRight></CartRight>
      </CartItems>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Cart;
